strings: <voice_0x01000B11><se_high>Accuracy: We were worried about seafood and asked to wait.
<voice_0x01000B12><se_high>Accuracy: I think you should rest and buy some food before you leave.
<voice_0x01000B13><se_high>Accuracy: I'm waiting here for you, don't wait! is busy
<voice_0x01000B14><se_high>Accuracy: Actually <most_heroic> I need to ask you something before I leave.
<voice_0x01000B15><se_high>Accuracy: Do you love dormouse as much as I do? We are fighting for the same reason.
<voice_0x01000B16><se_high>Accuracy: I thought why not give it a try together? It's been a long time since I've been interested in magic. But I still have a lot to learn. What do you think
<voice_0x01000B17><se_high>Accuracy: Aren't they the same? Yes, I am very happy, this is an important decision.
<voice_0x01000B18><se_high>Accuracy: But sorry, once you've made your decision. You can't go wrong.
<voice_0x01000B19><se_high>Accuracy: Yes, then I will tell you without asking <most_heroic>. I want to join your group!
<voice_0x01000B1C><se_low>King of tricks: Where do you think you'd be without me and my pretty princess?
<voice_0x01000B1D><se_low>Head of technology: Over! hit! Ready to leave the siding bridge!
